    public class PasswordChangeRequestFactory<A extends AppUser>
extends AbstractUserRequestFactory<A,PasswordChangeRequestFactory.PasswordChangeRequest>
    Holds an one use id-string associated with a user for resetting the login password. if known the current encrypted password is also stored and the tag won't match unlesss this is unchanged preventing the tag from being used once the password has been changed.
